<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - ضَرَبَه بجُمْع يده على ذَقْنه؛ لكَمه <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{فَوَكَزَهُ مُوسَى فَقَضَى عَلَيْهِ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• وكَز الشَّخصَ بالرُّمْح:</span> طعنَه به.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>